<div class="vt_brief">
<h2>Common Book Project goals</h2>
<ul><li>Established in 1998 to enrich the first-year experience and create a sense of community for undergraduate students.</li><li>Encourages conversation among faculty and students of various disciplines around a common text.</li></ul><p><a href="http://www.commonbook.vt.edu/content/prev_common_book.html">See previous Common Book selections</a>.</p></div>
